5. Explicit Permission: Paid Implementation / Consulting
--------------------------------------------------------
Notwithstanding Sections 4.1 and 4.2, You MAY charge for Professional Services related to the Software,
provided that ALL of the following are true:

(a) any copy of the Software or Derivative Works You provide to the customer is provided at no charge
under this License;

(b) the customer is not charged a license fee, subscription fee, access fee, or usage fee for the
Software itself;

(c) the Software is deployed and operated in the Customer Environment (i.e., the customer controls
the environment and can run the Software without You).

For clarity: charging for “setup”, “migration”, “integration”, “training”, “support”, or similar
Professional Services is allowed if the Software itself remains free of charge and is not provided
as a paid Hosted Service.

